Name: RaspberryMatic
Description: :house: A lightweight, buildroot-based Linux operating system alternative for your CCU3, ELV-Charly or for running your CloudFree "homematicIP CCU" IoT smarthome central as a pure virtual appliance (under Proxmox VE, Home Assistant, LXC, Docker/OCI Kubernetes/K8s, etc.) or on a dedicated device like RaspberryPi, Tinkerboard, ODROID, intelNUC, etc..
